tourBios.carHigh: 2015: T20 at the California Qualifying Tournament shooting rounds of 67-79-74-74.
tourBios.personal: Favorite course he's played is Cypress Point and hopes to play Augusta National someday...His favorite pro sports teams are the San Fransisco 49ers and Giants, as well as the San Jose Sharks...Dream foursome would include Tiger Woods, Jack Nicklaus and Arnold Palmer...Twitter name is @mattpini.

dyn.dynResults: His best finish on the Mackenzie Tour-PGA T was T51st in 2015 at the Staal Foundation Open presented by Tbaytel.
